originalText.text: Our organization's office has been in business with Plants Le Bacle for years and our relationship has been wonderful. They are thorough, friendly, and very professional. Our office plants are tended to with care and precision, and their customer service is exceptional. Additionally, we were also very appreciative of how they revived/replaced our entire plant inventory during the pandemic once we began to migrate back into the office. One of our longest standing vendors and we value them greatly!

originalText.text: We have been using Plants Lebacle for plant care in our office for a few years now. Michael and Tenzin have been amazing! During the pandemic he walked me through how to care for our plants until we were able to bring vendors back in the office. Tenzin is the plant guru and has kept our plant thriving. If you are looking for Plant care please check this company out. They have amazing customer service and you can't go wrong.
